      • findObstacleGraph

        public static <S extends Segment> java.util.ArrayList<Pair<S,S>> findObstacleGraph(java.util.ArrayList<S> segments)
        Finds the obstacle graph of the given ArrayList of OrthogonalSegment segments.
        Type Parameters:
        S - The segment class with which this obstacle graph will work.
        Parameters:
        segments - the vertical segments for which to find the obstacle graph
        Returns:
        an ArrayList of pairs of vertical segments, with each pair corresponding to an edge in the obstacle graph going from the first segment of the pair to the second.
